## 🚨 **COMMON MISTAKES TO AVOID**

### **NAVIGATION MISTAKES**
```
❌ Creating pages without navigation
❌ Missing navigation in mobile view
❌ Inconsistent navigation across pages
❌ No clear way to navigate between sections
❌ Broken links hoặc missing pages
❌ Navigation hidden hoặc hard to find
```

### **USER EXPERIENCE MISTAKES**
```
❌ Focusing only on individual components
❌ Ignoring user journey end-to-end
❌ Not testing navigation flow
❌ Missing responsive navigation
❌ Poor information hierarchy
❌ Inconsistent design patterns
```

### **QUALITY CONTROL MISTAKES**
```
❌ Approving without navigation testing
❌ Not validating user journey
❌ Ignoring accessibility requirements
❌ Missing responsive testing
❌ Not checking cross-browser compatibility
❌ Approving incomplete deliverables
```

